---
title: Pork Loin & Crumbed Pumpkin with Salad & Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: Our new fan favourite in the HelloFresh kitchen (and undoubtedly in yours too) - the crumbed butternut pumpkin, or what we prefer to call, the ‘crumpkin’. The whole dish goes down a treat, but let’s just say we know which part you’ll be reaching for first!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-loin-crumbed-pumpkin-88f60cde.jpg
